            "id": 6009676,
            "title": "〈大立光股東會〉完成董事改選 林恩平：考慮增加女性董事並強化ESG",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>光學元件股王大立光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3008:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3008\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3008-TW</a>) 今 (6) 日由董事林恩平主持召開 股東會並完成董事改選，林恩平在答覆股東提問指出，大立光會考慮增加女性董事；同時，對於與德商對軟體侵權爭議案，大立光對此案強調已進入司法程序，司法如何判，大立光依判決接受，不會影響生產。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009676%2Fl%2F43c1f131df69b4759c6a4f94281edaec.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009676%2Fl%2F43c1f131df69b4759c6a4f94281edaec.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009676%2Fl%2F43c1f131df69b4759c6a4f94281edaec.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009676%2Fl%2F43c1f131df69b4759c6a4f94281edaec.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009676%2Fl%2F43c1f131df69b4759c6a4f94281edaec.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009676%2Fl%2F43c1f131df69b4759c6a4f94281edaec.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009676%2Fl%2F43c1f131df69b4759c6a4f94281edaec.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009676%2Fl%2F43c1f131df69b4759c6a4f94281edaec.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009676%2Fl%2F43c1f131df69b4759c6a4f94281edaec.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009676%2Fl%2F43c1f131df69b4759c6a4f94281edaec.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009676%2Fl%2F43c1f131df69b4759c6a4f94281edaec.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009676%2Fl%2F43c1f131df69b4759c6a4f94281edaec.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009676%2Fl%2F43c1f131df69b4759c6a4f94281edaec.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009676%2Fl%2F43c1f131df69b4759c6a4f94281edaec.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009676%2Fl%2F43c1f131df69b4759c6a4f94281edaec.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009676%2Fl%2F43c1f131df69b4759c6a4f94281edaec.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009676%2Fl%2F43c1f131df69b4759c6a4f94281edaec.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">大立光6日召開股東會，圖左為總經理黃有執，右爲董事長林恩平。(鉅亨網記者張欽發攝)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>今天的大立光今天股東會完成董事改選，新一屆董事為茂鈺紀念股份有限公司代表人林恩舟及林恩平、梁忠仁、謝銘原、黃有執、陳俊明；而新任獨立董事為林進芳、張光道、李淑憫。林恩平表示，有規劃未來將增加女性董事。同時，大立光也強調對 ESG 的各項議題進行努力。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>大立光 2025 年第一季財報營收 145.79 億元毛利率 54.63%，季減 4.45 個百分點，年增 5.48 個百分點，稅後純益 64.43 億元，季減 25.74%，年增 5.44%，每股純益爲 48.28 元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>而大立光最新的營收顯示，大立光 5 月營收 32.38 億元，探 18 個月來新低，月減 25.98%，年減 7.11%，由進入季節性淡季加上因新舊機產品交替，造成 5 月營收的下滑，預估 6 月因少量新機種出貨，預估客戶端拉貨動能回升，累計前 5 月營收 221.47 億元，年增 21.31%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
