            "id": 6009679,
            "title": "〈焦點股〉鴻準5月營收年增2倍、Switch 2銷售助攻 價量齊揚攻季線",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>鴻準 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2354:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2354\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2354-TW</a>)5 月營收 147.54 億元，年增超過 2 倍，連續 8 個月呈現年增，加上任天堂新機 Switch 2 昨 (5) 日正式在日本、美國等市場開賣，全球玩家搶購，開出銷售紅盤，激勵鴻準今 (6) 日價量齊揚，攻上季線。 </p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009679%2Fl%2F4da5c0de4cb37dabfa571a6c2d042785.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009679%2Fl%2F4da5c0de4cb37dabfa571a6c2d042785.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009679%2Fl%2F4da5c0de4cb37dabfa571a6c2d042785.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009679%2Fl%2F4da5c0de4cb37dabfa571a6c2d042785.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009679%2Fl%2F4da5c0de4cb37dabfa571a6c2d042785.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009679%2Fl%2F4da5c0de4cb37dabfa571a6c2d042785.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009679%2Fl%2F4da5c0de4cb37dabfa571a6c2d042785.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009679%2Fl%2F4da5c0de4cb37dabfa571a6c2d042785.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009679%2Fl%2F4da5c0de4cb37dabfa571a6c2d042785.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009679%2Fl%2F4da5c0de4cb37dabfa571a6c2d042785.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009679%2Fl%2F4da5c0de4cb37dabfa571a6c2d042785.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009679%2Fl%2F4da5c0de4cb37dabfa571a6c2d042785.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009679%2Fl%2F4da5c0de4cb37dabfa571a6c2d042785.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009679%2Fl%2F4da5c0de4cb37dabfa571a6c2d042785.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009679%2Fl%2F4da5c0de4cb37dabfa571a6c2d042785.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009679%2Fl%2F4da5c0de4cb37dabfa571a6c2d042785.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009679%2Fl%2F4da5c0de4cb37dabfa571a6c2d042785.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">鴻準5月營收年增2倍、Switch 2銷售助攻，價量齊揚攻季線。(圖：擷取自任天堂官網)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>鴻準早盤以 62 元開高，盤中最高漲至 63.6 元，漲逾 4%，截至 9 點 40 分，股價暫報 61.8 元，漲幅約 2.49%，一舉站回季線，成交爆量超過 2.5 萬張。至於三大法人近日籌碼動向，三大法人本周至今合計賣超 3789 張。 </p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>鴻準 5 月營收 147.54 億元，月增 14.46%，年增 2.5 倍，連續 8 個月呈現年增，且寫下 4 年半以來新高；累計今年前 5 月營收 576.17 億元，年增 2.52 倍。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>即便任天堂已提前備貨，但仍供不應求，而鴻準身為 Switch 2 的機殼與組裝獨家供應商，在 Switch 2 銷售熱潮帶動下，法人看好鴻準持續受惠。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
